{"tid":1664244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大帽山離奇出現黃牛屍體 警指：極為可疑 要主動調查","createTime":"2019-10-20T03:28:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T11:27:01.000Z","uid":28114,"like":330,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":131,"replies":[{"pid":"cf8d7e9f942c428f91b29a52b36745a8f7035eb8","tid":1664244,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T03:28:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://juicy-news.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2019-10-20-%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%8812.40.24-848x521.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjuicy-news.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%259C%2596-2019-10-20-%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%258D%258812.40.24-848x521.png&h=e13d6cdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大帽山發生虐牛疑雲！今晨(19日)9時許，有漁護署人員報案，指荃灣大帽山近天氣雷達站，有一頭黃牛伏屍在引水道沙井內。警方聯同相關部門人員到場，將牛屍吊回路邊調查，證實該頭為成年雄性黃牛，約12歲，身長約1.8米，體重約200公斤，屍體頸部及大腿內側有傷，身體亦有被繩綁過的痕迹，極為可疑。<br />\n警方連同愛護動物協會人員在附近山坡仔細調查，沿山路發現有血漬及拖拉痕迹，更在山上檢獲繩索、手套及黑色膠袋，警方懷疑有人將牛隻綑綁，並強行拖下山坡，致牛隻失足墮坡跌進沙井，警方一度將案件暫列虐待動物。<br />\n惟警方及後向漁護署了解後，得悉該署牛隻管理隊人員，昨日(18日)在大帽山車道旁的護土牆發現該頭黃牛，疑牠由高處墮下致下身癱瘓，基於動物福利考慮，該牛被人道處理。惟人員企圖移走牛屍時，不慎將牛屍跌進路旁引水道，致今日才處理，引起誤會。<br />\n資料顯示，去年6月7日，大帽山發生一宗駭人小牛遭虐殺案，一隻小牛被掏空內臟，掛屍於近雷達站對開的標距柱上。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191019/photo/bkn-20191019115606789-1019_00822_001_04b.jpg?20191019230523\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191019%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20191019115606789-1019_00822_001_04b.jpg%3F20191019230523&h=f2a5a4a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191019/bkn-20191019115606789-1019_00822_001.html?fbclid=IwAR3GqaPKF5sxhtjFFAK4PWpCPEKkE1CG84Q-O6vGwDvBIB_GTbsjTyrdgYg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191019%2Fbkn-20191019115606789-1019_00822_001.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3GqaPKF5sxhtjFFAK4PWpCPEKkE1CG84Q-O6vGwDvBIB_GTbsjTyrdgYg&d=kavsisi6QTOS4EBqYfxwcy9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=c99d805f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191019/bkn-20191019115606789-1019_00822_001.html?fbclid=IwAR3GqaPKF5sxhtjFFAK4PWpCPEKkE1CG84Q-O6vGwDvBIB_GTbsjTyrdgYg</a>"},{"pid":"aa7bc94f77b6fde88a3344d1ba4deb5fd7672fea","tid":1664244,"uid":28114,"like":1103,"dislike":4,"score":1099,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T03:28:54.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，出現裸屍就WFC"},{"pid":"71930eeef7abcbf6731056cf4f50d967943792c0","tid":1664244,"uid":232845,"like":1428,"dislike":1,"score":1427,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T03:30:13.000Z","msg":"牛死就要調查<br />\n人死就收隊飲茶"},{"pid":"f7707064138013e78acd4342a37b4c00344ac2cb","tid":1664244,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T03:30:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9d9877e0213238c1aa69704bfd415d7e3c95e1a","tid":1664244,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T03:30:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04e01492095839ccf5dda0a95d356c68da348556","tid":1664244,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T03:30:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56deb6b08a0757b7294fd79b9e87ed3e1e51353e","tid":1664244,"uid":202340,"like":508,"dislike":15,"score":493,"citedBy":11,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T03:31:22.000Z","msg":"牛b 死了"},{"pid":"d81f10c2f1e5dad14a0b6b751f1f4375852e76ca","tid":1664244,"uid":21398,"like":311,"dislike":0,"score":311,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T03:32:09.000Z","msg":"牛死就可疑？<br />\n人死就唔可疑？<br />\n屌你老母死黑警！"},{"pid":"817c0dc3b1b0109919e21f52c0ce9ad7c22797cd","tid":1664244,"uid":49144,"like":117,"dislike":0,"score":117,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T03:33:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人的性命連動物都不如<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{